com.googlecode.jmxtrans.model.output

Class LibratoWriter

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.googlecode.jmxtrans.model.output.BaseOutputWriter
      • com.googlecode.jmxtrans.model.output.LibratoWriter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    OutputWriter

    public class LibratoWriter
extends BaseOutputWriter
    This writer is a port of the LibratoWriter from the embedded-jmxtrans project.

    Librato Metrics

    This implementation uses POST /v1/metrics HTTP API.

    Settings:

    • "url": Librato server URL. Optional, default value: "https://metrics-api.librato.com/v1/metrics".
    • "username": Librato username. Mandatory
    • "token": Librato token. Mandatory
    • "libratoApiTimeoutInMillis": read timeout of the calls to Librato HTTP API. Optional, default value: 1000.
    Author:
    Cyrille Le Clerc
